c: 16
v: 93
t: "“Ndipo Allah akadafuna, ndithu akadakuchitani kukhala gulu limodzi, (nonsenu mukadamumvera monga momwe adawachitira angelo, koma adakupatsani ufulu kuti muchite chimene mufuna); komatu amamulekelera kusokera amene wamfuna, ndipo amamuongola wamfuna; ndipo, ndithu mudzafunsidwa pa zomwe munkachita"